This paper is likely to belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) category as it focuses on program comprehension and refactoring of software systems. It also employs machine learning techniques to improve the performance of these tasks. The paper also discusses the use of multi-view learning, which involves combining information from different sources, making the categories cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.SD (Software Development) likely as well. Finally, the paper deals with source code, which suggests that it could also belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL) category.
